# ğŸ“± React Native To-Do App with Authentication

A feature-rich **To-Do List Mobile Application** built using **React Native CLI with TypeScript**, featuring **user authentication**, **task management**, and a **clean, modern UI**.

This project was developed as part of an assignment to demonstrate understanding of **React Native fundamentals**, **state management**, and **authentication workflows**.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

### ğŸ” User Authentication
- Register using **email and password**
- Login for existing users
- Secure authentication using **Firebase Authentication**
- Persistent login session
- Logout functionality

### ğŸ“ Task Management
- Add tasks with:
  - Title
  - Description
  - Priority (Low / Medium / High)
  - Created date & time
- View a list of all tasks
- Mark tasks as **completed**
- Delete tasks
- Visual task status:
  - Checkbox toggle
  - Strikethrough for completed tasks
  - â€œCompletedâ€ label for clarity

### ğŸ¨ User Interface
- Clean, modern dark-themed UI
- Card-based task layout
- Priority display
- Floating action button for adding tasks

